        public String createLocalEntry(Map<String,Object> registryMap)
                        throws FederationAdminException
        Description copied from interface: FederationAdminMBean
        Create a local entry in the registry catalog for the given object map. The map will be converted to a RegistryPackageType using the RegistryPackageWebConverter. The resulting RegistryPackageType will be passed to FederationAdminService#addLocalEntry to create the entry.
        Specified by:
        createLocalEntry in interface FederationAdminMBean
        Returns:
        Id of the created metacard.
        Throws:
        FederationAdminException - Passes exception thrown by FederationAdminServiceImpl

      • createLocalEntry

        public String createLocalEntry(String base64EncodedXmlData)
                        throws FederationAdminException
        Description copied from interface: FederationAdminMBean
        Create a local entry in the registry catalog for the given string. The String provided is an Base64 encoded representation of a registry package xml. The RegistryTransformer transforms the Base64 decode stream into a registry metacard.
        Specified by:
        createLocalEntry in interface FederationAdminMBean
        Parameters:
        base64EncodedXmlData - Base64 encoded registry package xml.
        Returns:
        Id of the created metacard
        Throws:
        FederationAdminException - If Base64 decoding of the string fails If the RegistryTransformer can't convert the stream into a metacard Passes exceptions thrown by FederationAdminServiceImpl
